<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>النَّشْأَةَ الْأُخْرى الإحياء بعد الإماتة.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة النجم <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> : الآيات ٤٨ الى ٥٤]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ أَغْنى وَأَقْنى <span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ رَبُّ الشِّعْرى <span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> وَأَنَّهُ أَهْلَكَ عاداً الْأُولى <span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> وَثَمُودَ فَما أَبْقى <span class="c2">(٥١)</span> وَقَوْمَ نُوحٍ مِنْ قَبْلُ إِنَّهُمْ كانُوا هُمْ أَظْلَمَ وَأَطْغى <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ أَهْوى <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> فَغَشَّاها ما غَشَّى <span class="c2">(٥٤)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤٨-<span class="c5"> وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ أَغْنى وَأَقْنى:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ وحده.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَغْنى أعطى ما يكفى.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَأَقْنى وأرضى بما يقتنى ويدخر.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٤٩-<span class="c5"> وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ رَبُّ الشِّعْرى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَنَّهُ هُوَ وحده.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">رَبُّ الشِّعْرى الكوكب العظيم المسمى:</span> الشعرى، وهو ألمع نجم يرى فى السماء.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٥٠-<span class="c5"> وَأَنَّهُ أَهْلَكَ عاداً الْأُولى:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَأَنَّهُ وحده.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عاداً الْأُولى قوم هود.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥١-<span class="c5"> وَثَمُودَ فَما أَبْقى:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَثَمُودَ قوم صالح.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَما أَبْقى عليهم.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٥٢-<span class="c5"> وَقَوْمَ نُوحٍ مِنْ قَبْلُ إِنَّهُمْ كانُوا هُمْ أَظْلَمَ وَأَطْغى:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَظْلَمَ أكثر ظلما.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَأَطْغى أكثر طغيانا.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٥٣-<span class="c5"> وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ أَهْوى:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَةَ يعنى أن قوم لوط ائتفكت بهم قراهم، أي انقلبت وصار عاليها سافلها.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>أَهْوى جعلها تهوى وتنقلب.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٥٤-<span class="c5"> فَغَشَّاها ما غَشَّى:</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>